title: Dishwasher Motor
description: Dishwasher Motor ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 21 Reviews PartSelect Number PS5136127 Manufacturer Part Number W10537869 Also know as a diverter valve. This diverter motor is for dishwashers. Diverter motor controls the flow of water to the spray arms. Unplug the dishwasher and shut off the water supply before installing this part. Wear work gloves to protect your hands.

installationInstructions.author: Dennis from PORTAGE, MI
installationInstructions.title: Diverter valve was leaking.
installationInstructions.content: After shutting off electricity, lay dishwasher on it's side (use a towel to absorb any water) then just use nut driver to remove faulty valve.
